    "attributes": {
        "action": "Ban schools from requiring students to take Religious Education GCSE",
        "additional_details": "Not everyone wants to study Religious Education as a GCSE and students shouldn't be forced to study a subject they have no interest in, especially when the subject is optional in most schools.",
        "background": "Some schools require their students to take Religious Education as a GCSE, even though this is not a compulsory subject for Key Stage 4. We want this to be banned.",
